criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Primary caregivers who identify difficulties managing the behavior of a child between
             the ages of 2 and 11 years old.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Primary caregivers of children with serious neurodevelopmental or cognitive disorders
             diagnosed;

          -  Primary caregivers of children institucionalized;

          -  Primary caregivers who do not comprehend, read or write in portuguese;

          -  Primary caregivers inability to commit to weekly sessions.
